- Open the terminal and hit command "npm install"
- Then run "npm start" in the terminal
- Open a second terminal and run command "json-server -p 4000 --watch db.json"
- You will now be abled to see the site at "http://localhost:3000".
- You can add patient, get list of patients, delete patient and update patients.
- Please select a patient on home screen to get details of it.
- You will find all the details with patient's illness, current condition, medicines given as per date, how many days of dose required for patients and all.
- You can apply medicine on daily basis to the respective patient.
- You will be get notified if your medicine doesn't match with suggested medicine at the time of patient entry.
- This is how you can manage your patient's records.
